==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Exactor
<hw>Ex*act"or</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.: cf. F.
<ets>exacteur</ets>.]</ety> <def>One who exacts or demands by authority
or right; hence, an extortioner; also, one unreasonably severe in
injunctions or demands.</def> <rj><au>Jer. Taylor.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

